Bob Schultz is a happily married man who loves walking around Davis and writing about the interesting people and places he encounters around town.  You can follow his wanderings by going directly to Walking Bob http://www.davislifemagazine.com/funstuff/people/walkingbob or finding Davis Life Magazine and putting in the keywords “Walking Bob.”  He also teaches at Brandman University in Roseville and is involved in many facets of the mission of Davis Community Church.
